 South (Josh Turner album)|Deep South]]''\n| [[Josh Turner]]\n| MCA Nashville\n| March 10\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[The Devil Don't Sleep]]''\n| [[Brantley Gilbert]]\n| Valory Music Group\n| January 27\n|-\n| align=center| 2\n| ''[[Did It for the Party]]''\n| [[Big & Rich]]\n| Big & Rich/Thirty Tigers\n| September 15\n|-\n| align=center| 5\n| ''Dirty South''\n| [[Lucas Hoge]]\n| Rebel Engine Entertainment\n| July 21\n|-\n| align=center| 7\n| ''[[Everybody (Chris Janson album)|Everybody]]''\n| [[Chris Janson]]\n| Warner Bros. Nashville\n| September 22\n|-\n| align=center| 4\n| ''[[Every Little Thing (album)|Every Little Thing]]''\n| [[Carly Pearce]]\n| Big Machine\n| October 13\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[From A Room: Volume 1]]''\n| [[Chris Stapleton]]\n| Mercury Nashville\n| May 5\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[From A Room: Volume 2]]''\n| Chris Stapleton\n| Mercury Nashville\n| December 1\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[God's Problem Child]]''\n| [[Willie Nelson]]\n| Legacy\n| April 28\n|-\n| align=center| 5\n| ''[[Gold (Jessie James Decker EP)|Gold]]''\n| [[Jessie James Decker]]\n| Epic Records\n| February 17\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[Happy Endings (Old Dominion album)|Happy Endings]]''\n| [[Old Dominion (band)|Old Dominion]]\n| RCA Nashville\n| August 25\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[Heart Break (Lady Antebellum album)|Heart Break]]''\n| [[Lady Antebellum]]\n| Capitol Nashville\n| June 9\n|-\n| align=center| 6\n| ''[[I Don't Believe We've Met]]''\n| [[Danielle Bradbery]]\n| BMLG\n| December 1\n|-\n| align=center| 6\n| ''If Not for You''\n| [[Joey Feek]]\n| Farmhouse Recordings/Capitol Christian\n| April 7\n|-\n| align=center| 10\n| ''King of Dixie''\n| [[Upchurch (musician)|Upchurch]]\n| Redneck Nation\n| November 10\n|-\n| align=center| 6\n| ''[[Lambs & Lions]]''\n| [[Chase Rice]]\n| Broken Bow\n| November 17\n|-\n| align=center| 7\n| [[Lee Brice (album)|''Lee Brice'']]\n| [[Lee Brice]]\n| Curb\n| November 3\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[Life Changes (Th