e Adkins album)|Something's Going On]]''\n| [[Trace Adkins]]\n| Wheelhouse\n| March 31\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[Southern Girl City Lights]]''\n| [[Jessie James Decker]]\n| Epic Records\n| October 13\n|-\n| align=center| 4\n| ''[[Sweet Southern Sugar]]''\n| [[Kid Rock]]\n| Top Dog/BMG\n| November 3\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[Texoma Shore]]''\n| [[Blake Shelton]]\n| Warner Bros. Nashville\n| November 3\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[This One's for You (Luke Combs album)|This One's for You]]''\n| [[Luke Combs]]\n| Columbia Nashville\n| June 2\n|-\n| align=center| 3\n| ''Timeless''\n| [[Home Free (group)|Home Free]]\n| Columbia\n| September 22\n|-\n| align=center| 3\n| ''[[Unapologetically]]''\n| [[Kelsea Ballerini]]\n| Black River\n| November 3\n|-\n| align=center| 2\n| ''Vaquero''\n| [[Aaron Watson]]\n| BIG Label\n| February 24\n|-\n| align=center| 4\n| ''The Voice: The Complete Season 12 Collection''\n| Lauren Duski\n| Republic\n| May 19\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[Welcome Home (Zac Brown Band album)|Welcome Home]]''\n| [[Zac Brown Band]]\n| Elektra\n| May 12\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''What Makes You Country''\n| [[Luke Bryan]]\n| Capitol Nashville\n| December 8\n|-\n| align=center| 2\n| ''[[When the Good Guys Win]]''\n| [[Granger Smith]]\n| Wheelhouse\n| October 27\n|-\n| align=center| 2\n| ''[[When Was the Last Time]]''\n| [[Darius Rucker]]\n| Capitol Nashville\n| October 20\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[WildHorse]]''\n| [[RaeLynn]]\n| Warner Bros. Nashville\n| March 24\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[Windy City (album)|Windy City]]''\n| [[Alison Krauss]]\n| Capitol\n| February 17\n|-\n| align=center| 4\n| ''[[Words (Sara Evans album)|Words]]''\n| [[Sara Evans]]\n| Concord Music/Born to Fly\n| July 21\n|-\n| align=center| 5\n| ''[[Yours (Russell Dickerson album)|Yours]]''\n| [[Russell Dickerson]]\n| Triple Tigers\n| October 13\n|}\n\n=== Other top albums ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=45|<small>US</small>\n! Album\n! Artist\n! Record Labe