 You]]''\n| [[Luke Combs]]\n| Columbia Nashville\n| June 2\n|-\n| align=center| 3\n| ''Timeless''\n| [[Home Free (group)|Home Free]]\n| Columbia\n| September 22\n|-\n| align=center| 3\n| ''[[Unapologetically]]''\n| [[Kelsea Ballerini]]\n| Black River\n| November 3\n|-\n| align=center| 2\n| ''Vaquero''\n| [[Aaron Watson]]\n| BIG Label\n| February 24\n|-\n| align=center| 4\n| ''The Voice: The Complete Season 12 Collection''\n| Lauren Duski\n| Republic\n| May 19\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[Welcome Home (Zac Brown Band album)|Welcome Home]]''\n| [[Zac Brown Band]]\n| Elektra\n| May 12\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''What Makes You Country''\n| [[Luke Bryan]]\n| Capitol Nashville\n| December 8\n|-\n| align=center| 2\n| ''[[When the Good Guys Win]]''\n| [[Granger Smith]]\n| Wheelhouse\n| October 27\n|-\n| align=center| 2\n| ''[[When Was the Last Time]]''\n| [[Darius Rucker]]\n| Capitol Nashville\n| October 20\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[WildHorse]]''\n| [[RaeLynn]]\n| Warner Bros. Nashville\n| March 24\n|-\n| align=center| 1\n| ''[[Windy City (album)|Windy City]]''\n| [[Alison Krauss]]\n| Capitol\n| February 17\n|-\n| align=center| 4\n| ''[[Words (Sara Evans album)|Words]]''\n| [[Sara Evans]]\n| Concord Music/Born to Fly\n| July 21\n|-\n| align=center| 5\n| ''[[Yours (Russell Dickerson album)|Yours]]''\n| [[Russell Dickerson]]\n| Triple Tigers\n| October 13\n|}\n\n=== Other top albums ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=45|<small>US</small>\n! Album\n! Artist\n! Record Label\n! Release Date\n|-\n| align=center| 24\n| ''15 Years: The Wild Ride''\n| [[Casey Donahew]]\n| Almost Country\n| October 6\n|-\n| align=center| 14\n| ''50 Years of Blonde on Blonde''\n| [[Old Crow Medicine Show]]\n| Columbia Nashville\n| April 28\n|-\n| align=center| 22\n| ''[[27861]]''\n| [[Parmalee]]\n| Stoney Creek\n| July 21\n|-\n| align=center| 12\n| ''All American Made''\n| [[Margo Price]]\n| Third Man\n| October 20\n|-\n| align=center| 45\n| ''American Grandstand''\n| [[Rhonda Vincent]] & [[Daryle Singletary]]\n| Upper Management\n| July 7\n|-\n| align=center| 42\n| ''The Blame'' (EP)\n| Sam Grow\n| Ole\n| May 19\n|-\n| align=center| 13\n| ''Backroads'' (EP)\n| Taylor Ray Holbrook\n| TaylorRayMade\n| April 21\n|-\n| align=center| 19\n| ''Baptized in Bourbon''\n| [[Moonshine Bandits]]\n| Backroad-Average Joe's\n| March 3\n|-\n| align=center| 37\n| ''Bidin' My Time''\n| [[Chris Hillman]]\n| Rounder\n| September 22\n|-\n| align=center| 43\n| ''Black & White Night 30''\n| [[Roy Orbison]]\n| Legacy\n| February 24\n|-\n| align=center| 31\n| ''Brand New Day''\n| [[The Mavericks]]\n| Mono Mundo\n| March 31\n|-\n| align=center| 28\n| ''Close Ties''\n| [[Rodney Crowell]]\n| New West\n| March 31\n|-\n| align=center| 50\n| ''Colter Wall''\n| Colter Wall\n| Young Mary's Record Co.\n| May 12\n|-\n| align=center| 43\n| ''DCX MMXVI Live''\n| [[Dixie Chicks]]\n| Columbia\n| September 1\n|-\n| align=center| 17\n| ''Fingerprints''\n| [[Eli Young Band]]\n| Valory Music Co.\n| June 16\n|-\n| align=center| 16\n| ''Good Ole Days''\n| [[Tracy Lawrence]]\n| Lawrence Music Group\n| November 10\n|-\n| align=center| 46\n| ''Greatest Hits''\n| [[Jake Owen]]\n| RCA Nashville\n| November 24\n|-\n| align=center| 41\n| ''[[Highway Queen]]''\n| [[Nikki Lane]]\n| New West\n| February 17\n|-\n| align=center| 20\n| ''[[I Believe in You (Dolly Parton album)|I Believe in You]]''\n| [[Dolly Parton]]\n| Dolly Records\n| October 13\n|-\n| align=center| 26\n| ''Laws of Gravity''\n| [[Infamous Stringdusters]]\n| Compass\n| January 13\n|-\n| align=center| 14\n| ''Legacy''\n| [[The Cadillac Three]]\n| Big Machine\n| August 25\n|-\n| align=center| 37\n| ''[[The Lonely, the Lonesome & the Gone]]''\n| [[Lee Ann Womack]]\n| Sugar Hill\n| October 27\n|-\n| align=center| 26\n| ''A Love So Beautiful''\n| [[Roy Orbison]] with the [[Royal Philharmonic Orchestra]]\n| Legacy\n| November 3\n|-\n| align=center| 35\n| ''Lukas Nelson & Promise of the Real''\n| [[Lukas Nelson & Promise of the Real]]\n|